&lt;h2 class="relative group"&gt;Why Visit Split?
 &lt;div id="why-visit-split" class="anchor"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 
 &lt;span
 class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none"&gt;
 &lt;a class="text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline" href="#why-visit-split" aria-label="Anchor"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
