&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://ferry.techpawz.com/posts/hvar-to-split-ferry/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"&gt;Split&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://cruise.techpawz.com/posts/dubrovnik_shore-excursions/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"&gt;Croatia&lt;/a&gt;, is a vibrant coastal city that beautifully marries history with modernity. Nestled along the stunning Adriatic Sea, it boasts a rich history that dates back to the Roman Empire. The city is home to the magnificent Diocletian&amp;rsquo;s Palace, a UNESCO World Heritage site that forms the heart of Split and offers a glimpse into its storied past. As you wander through its ancient streets, you’ll encounter a mix of Roman ruins, medieval architecture, and a lively atmosphere that perfectly captures the essence of Mediterranean life.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>What to Know Before Visiting Dubrovnik: Insider Tips and Travel Advice</title><link>https://visa.techpawz.com/posts/dubrovnik-croatia/</link><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 10:32:28 +0700</pubDate><guid>https://visa.techpawz.com/posts/dubrovnik-croatia/</guid><description>&lt;script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-8772455780561463"
